#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#
# posicionamiento grid
"""
import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import ttk

ventana = tk.Tk()
ventana.title("GRID")
ventana.config(width=400, height=370)


caja1 = ttk.Entry()
caja1.grid(row=0, column=0) 


caja2 = ttk.Entry()
caja2.grid(row=1, column=1) 
# anclado de la fila y columna 2
label = ttk.Label(text="Hola")
label.grid(row=2, column=2, sticky="nsew", padx=100, pady=20)

# habilito el redimensionamiento automatico en la columna y fila 2

ventana.columnconfigure(2, weight=1)
ventana.rowconfigure(2, weight=1)

ventana.mainloop()
"""
# posicionamiento pack
import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import ttk

ventana = tk.Tk()
ventana.title("PACK")
ventana.config(width=400, height=300)

caja = ttk.Entry()
caja.pack(side=tk.LEFT)

etiqueta = ttk.Label(text="antes de la caja...")
etiqueta.pack(before=caja)

boton = ttk.Button(text="click me!")
boton.pack(after=etiqueta, padx=30, pady=50, ipadx=70, ipady=35)

caja2 = ttk.Entry()
caja2.pack(before=caja, expand=True, fill=tk.BOTH)

ventana.mainloop()

from hashlib import sha256
from time import sleep
MAX_NONCE = 100000000000

def SHA256(text):
    return sha256(text.encode("ascii")).hexdigest()

def mine(block_number, transactions, previous_hash, prefix_zeros):
    prefix_str = '0'*prefix_zeros
    for nonce in range(MAX_NONCE):
        text = str(block_number) + transactions + previous_hash + str(nonce)
        new_hash = SHA256(text)
        if new_hash.startswith(prefix_str):
            print(f"Yay! Successfully mined bitcoins with nonce value:{nonce}")
            return new_hash

    raise BaseException(f"Couldn't find correct has after trying {MAX_NONCE} times")

if __name__=='__main__':
    transactions='''
    Dhaval->Bhavin->20,
    Mando->Cara->45
    '''
    difficulty=4 # try changing this to higher number and you will see it will take more time for mining as difficulty increases
    import time
    start = time.time()
    sleep(3)
    print("started mining...")
    sleep(3)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("\/")
    sleep(2)
    new_hash = mine(5,transactions,'0000000a036944e29568d0cff17edbe038f81208fecf9a66be9a2b8321c6ec7', difficulty)
    sleep(2)
    total_time = str((time.time() - start))
    sleep(3)
    print(f"ending mining. Mining took: {total_time} seconds")
    sleep(2)
    print(new_hash)

<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace HamDx\Validation;

class MaidenheadAnalyzer
{
    public const RANGE_FIELD = 'A-R';
    public const RANGE_SQUARE = '0-9';
    public const RANGE_SUB_SQUARE = 'A-X';

    /** @var MaidenheadValidator */
    protected $validator;

    public function __construct(MaidenheadValidator $validator)
    {
        $this->validator = $validator;
    }

    /**
     * @param int|null $errorPosition approximate position of the error, if not known the validator is used
     */
    public function analyze(string $callsign, int $errorPosition = null): array
    {
        // if the position of the error is known, the locator cannot be valid
        $valid = ($errorPosition !== null ? false : null);

        // validation
        if ($errorPosition === null) {
            $valid = $this->validator->validate($callsign, $errorPosition);
        }

        if (!$valid) {
            $validPart = substr($callsign, 0, ($errorPosition - 1));
            $invalidPair = substr($callsign, ($errorPosition - 1), 2);

            // detect range for next pair validation
            $validRange = ((strlen($validPart) / 2) % 2 === 0 ? self::RANGE_SUB_SQUARE : self::RANGE_SQUARE);
            if ($errorPosition === 1) {
                $validRange = self::RANGE_FIELD;
            }

            $detail = [];

            // check both characters in the invalid pair
            for ($i = 0; $i < 2; $i++) {
                $currentChar = $invalidPair[$i] ?? ' '; // add space to correct for odd number of characters

                $isInvalidChar = (
                    ($validRange === self::RANGE_SQUARE && !is_numeric($currentChar))
                    || ($validRange !== self::RANGE_SQUARE
                        && (is_numeric($currentChar) || !$this->isCharInRange($currentChar, $validRange))
                    )
                );

                if ($isInvalidChar) {
                    $detail[] = [
                        'position' => $errorPosition + $i,
                        'character' => $currentChar,
                        'range' => $validRange,
                    ];
                }
            }

            return [
                'valid_part' => $validPart,
                'invalid_pair' => $invalidPair,
                'valid_range' => $validRange,
                'detail' => $detail,
            ];
        } else {
            return [];
        }
    }

    private function isCharInRange(string $char, string $range): bool
    {
        return (
            ord(strtoupper($char)) >= ord($range[0])
            && ord(strtoupper($char)) <= ord($range[2])
        );
    }
}

local modem = peripheral.wrap("back")
local startIP = 100
local endIP = 200
local serverName = "dhcp_server"

function saveData(name, ip, mac)
    -- Code pour enregistrer les donnes dans un fichier (vous pouvez personnaliser cette partie en fonction de vos besoins)
    -- Exemple : fs.open("/data.txt", "a").writeLine(serverName .. "," .. ip .. "," .. mac .. "," .. name).close()
end

function dhcpServer()
    print("Serveur DHCP " .. serverName .. " oprationnel. En attente de demandes d'adresse...")

    while true do
        local event, modemSide, senderChannel, replyChannel, message, senderDistance = os.pullEvent("modem_message")
        
        if message == "DHCP_DISCOVER" then
            local _, _, _, _, mac = event, modemSide, senderChannel, replyChannel, message, senderDistance
            local ip = "10.10.0." .. startIP
            startIP = startIP + 1

            if startIP > endIP then
                print("Erreur : Plus d'adresses IP disponibles pour le serveur " .. serverName .. ".")
                break
            end
            
            modem.transmit(replyChannel, replyChannel, "DHCP_OFFER," .. ip)
            
            -- Demander  la machine cliente d'envoyer son nom
            modem.transmit(replyChannel, replyChannel, "DHCP_NAME_REQUEST")
            
            local _, _, _, _, name = os.pullEvent("modem_message")
            
            saveData(name, ip, mac)

            print("Offre d'adresse envoye  la machine " .. name .. " avec l'adresse MAC : " .. mac)
            print("Serveur " .. serverName .. " - Adresse IP offerte : " .. ip .. " - Nom de l'hte : " .. name)
        end
    end
end

dhcpServer()

-- file_srv.lua - Gestionnaire de fichiers

local filesystemRoot = "/srv/"
local currentDirectory = filesystemRoot

-- Afficher la liste des fichiers du rpertoire courant
local function listFiles()
    term.clear()
    term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
    print("=== Fichiers dans le rpertoire courant ===")
    local files = fs.list(currentDirectory)
    for i, file in ipairs(files) do
        print(i .. ". " .. file)
    end
end

-- Gestionnaire de fichiers
local function fileManager()
    term.clear()
    term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
    print("=== Gestionnaire de fichiers ===")
    print("Rpertoire courant: " .. currentDirectory)
    print("1. Afficher les fichiers et dossiers")
    print("2. Crer un dossier")
    print("3. Crer un fichier")
    print("4. Lire un fichier")
    print("5. Supprimer un fichier ou dossier")
    print("6. Aller au rpertoire parent")
    print("7. Retour au menu principal")

    local choice = tonumber(read())

    if choice == 1 then
        listFiles()
        os.sleep(2)
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 2 then
        term.clear()
        term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
        print("=== Crer un dossier ===")
        print("Nom du dossier:")
        local folderName = read()
        fs.makeDir(currentDirectory .. folderName)
        print("Le dossier a t cr.")
        os.sleep(2)
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 3 then
        term.clear()
        term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
        print("=== Crer un fichier ===")
        print("Nom du fichier:")
        local fileName = read()
        local file = fs.open(currentDirectory .. fileName, "w")
        file.close()
        print("Le fichier a t cr.")
        os.sleep(2)
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 4 then
        listFiles()
        print("Choisissez un fichier  lire (0 pour annuler):")
        local fileChoice = tonumber(read())
        if fileChoice > 0 and fileChoice <= #fs.list(currentDirectory) then
            local files = fs.list(currentDirectory)
            local fileName = files[fileChoice]
            local file = fs.open(currentDirectory .. fileName, "r")
            local content = file.readAll()
            file.close()
            term.clear()
            term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
            print("=== Contenu du fichier ===")
            print(content)
            os.sleep(3)
        else
            print("Choix invalide.")
            os.sleep(2)
        end
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 5 then
        listFiles()
        print("Choisissez un fichier ou dossier  supprimer (0 pour annuler):")
        local fileChoice = tonumber(read())
        if fileChoice > 0 and fileChoice <= #fs.list(currentDirectory) then
            local files = fs.list(currentDirectory)
            local fileName = files[fileChoice]
            local path = currentDirectory .. fileName

            if fs.isDir(path) then
                print("Voulez-vous vraiment supprimer le dossier '" .. fileName .. "' ? (oui/non)")
            else
                print("Voulez-vous vraiment supprimer le fichier '" .. fileName .. "' ? (oui/non)")
            end

            local confirmation = read()
            if confirmation == "oui" then
                fs.delete(path)
                print("Le fichier ou dossier a t supprim.")
            else
                print("Suppression annule.")
            end
            os.sleep(2)
        else
            print("Choix invalide.")
            os.sleep(2)
        end
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 6 then
        if currentDirectory ~= filesystemRoot then
            currentDirectory = fs.getDir(currentDirectory)
        else
            print("Vous tes dj dans le rpertoire racine.")
            os.sleep(2)
        end
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 7 then
        return  -- Retour au menu principal
    else
        print("Choix invalide.")
        os.sleep(2)
        fileManager()
    end
end

fileManager()

local filesystemRoot = "/srv/"
local mainFile = "main.lua"
local usersFile = "users.txt"  -- Fichier contenant les noms d'utilisateur et les mots de passe

-- Ajouter un utilisateur au fichier users.txt
local function addUser(username, password)
    local users = {}

    -- Vrifier si le fichier existe et le lire s'il est prsent
    if fs.exists(filesystemRoot .. usersFile) then
        local file = fs.open(filesystemRoot .. usersFile, "r")
        users = textutils.unserialize(file.readAll())
        file.close()
    end

    -- Ajouter l'utilisateur
    users[username] = password

    -- Enregistrer les utilisateurs dans le fichier
    local file = fs.open(filesystemRoot .. usersFile, "w")
    file.write(textutils.serialize(users))
    file.close()

    print("Utilisateur ajout avec succs.")
end

title: main_srv
content:
-- Systme d'exploitation minimal pour Computercraft avec systme d'authentification

local filesystemRoot = "/srv/"
local mainFile = "main.lua"
local usersFile = "users.txt"  -- Fichier contenant les noms d'utilisateur et les mots de passe
local fileManagerFile = "file_srv.lua"  -- Fichier contenant le gestionnaire de fichiers

-- Fonction d'authentification de l'utilisateur
local function authenticate()
    term.clear()
    term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
    print("=== Authentification ===")
    print("Nom d'utilisateur:")
    local username = read()
    print("Mot de passe:")
    local password = read("*")

    -- Vrification des informations d'authentification ( amliorer dans une version complte)
    local users = {}
    local file = fs.open(filesystemRoot .. usersFile, "r")
    if file then
        users = textutils.unserialize(file.readAll())
        file.close()
    end

    if users[username] and users[username] == password then
        print("Authentification russie.")
        os.sleep(1)
        return true
    else
        print("Nom d'utilisateur ou mot de passe incorrect.")
        os.sleep(2)
        return false
    end
end

-- Appeler le gestionnaire de fichiers
local function callFileManager()
    local path = filesystemRoot .. fileManagerFile
    if fs.exists(path) then
        shell.run(path)
    else
        print("Le gestionnaire de fichiers n'existe pas.")
    end
end

-- Authentification de l'utilisateur avant le menu principal
local function mainLoop()
    local authenticated = false

    while not authenticated do
        authenticated = authenticate()
    end

    -- Aprs l'authentification russie, accder au menu principal
    while true do
        term.clear()
        term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
        print("=== Menu principal ===")
        print("1. Gestionnaire de fichiers")
        print("2. Configurer rseau")
        print("3. Quitter")

        local choice = tonumber(read())

        if choice == 1 then
            callFileManager()
        elseif choice == 2 then
            -- Configuration du rseau ( implmenter)
            print("Fonctionnalit  venir...")
            os.sleep(2)
        elseif choice == 3 then
            print("Au revoir !")
            break
        else
            print("Choix invalide.")
            os.sleep(2)
        end
    end
end

-- Dmarrage du systme d'exploitation
local function loadMainFile()
    local path = filesystemRoot .. mainFile
    if fs.exists(path) then
        shell.run(path)
    else
        print("Le fichier principal n'existe pas.")
    end
end

-- Crer le rpertoire /srv s'il n'existe pas
if not fs.exists(filesystemRoot) then
    fs.makeDir(filesystemRoot)
end

mainLoop()

content:
import cv2
def getDist(coord1, coord2):
    return ((coord1[0] - coord2[0]) ** 2 + (coord1[1] - coord2[1]) ** 2) ** 0.5

grayimg = cv2.imread("FourSpots.jpg", cv2.IMREAD_GRAYSCALE)
foundSpots = []                  # list of tuples of coordinates of top left corner of each dark spot
for row, aline in enumerate(grayimg):           # aline contains one horizontal line of pixels
    for col, pixel in enumerate(aline):         # pixel contains whiteness level of one pixel
        if pixel < 85:                          # Find a dark pixel
            for spot in foundSpots:
                if getDist((row, col), spot) < 50:
                    break                       # pixel is close to an already known spot
            else:
                foundSpots.append((row, col))      # Last loop did NOT end with break
baseDist = 0
num = len(foundSpots)
for x in range(num):            # Look at all combinations of 2 spots, and check their separation
    for y in range(x+1, num):
        d = getDist(foundSpots[x], foundSpots[y])
        if d > baseDist:
            baseDist = d                                    # keep the greatest distance
            basePair = (foundSpots[x], foundSpots[y])       # remember the base pair
otherSpots = [spot for spot in foundSpots if spot not in basePair]
pairs = ["A-C", "A-D", "B-C", "B-D"]
for i in basePair:
    for j in otherSpots:
        pc = (100 * getDist(i, j)) / baseDist
        print(f"{pairs.pop(0)} is {pc:.0f}% of A-B")

# Output:
# A-C is 81% of A-B
# A-D is 38% of A-B
# B-C is 44% of A-B
# B-D is 66% of A-B

import bpy
import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET
import os

# Funo para criar ou recuperar um material com base no nome
def get_material(name):
    material = bpy.data.materials.get(name)
    if material is None:
        material = bpy.data.materials.new(name)
        return material
    return None

# Funo para aplicar os materiais nos objetos
def apply_material_properties(material, properties):
    if material is None:
        return
    material.use_nodes = True
    principled_bsdf = material.node_tree.nodes.get("Principled BSDF")
    if 
    if "COLORBASE" in properties:
        principled_bsdf.inputs["Base Color"].default_value = properties["COLORBASE"]
    if "METALLIC" in properties:
        principled_bsdf.inputs[6].default_value = float(properties["METALLIC"])
    if "SPECULAR" in properties:
        principled_bsdf.inputs["Specular"].default_value = float(properties["SPECULAR"])
    if "ROUGHNESS" in properties:
        principled_bsdf.inputs["Roughness"].default_value = float(properties["ROUGHNESS"])
    if "TRANSPARENCY" in properties:
        principled_bsdf.inputs["Transmission"].default_value = float(properties["TRANSPARENCY"])
        material.use_screen_refraction = True
        material.refraction_depth = 0.03  # 30mm
    if "EMISSION" in properties:
        principled_bsdf.inputs[20].default_value = float(properties["EMISSION"])
    if "IOR" in properties:
        principled_bsdf.inputs["IOR"].default_value = float(properties["IOR"])
    # Verifica se h textura no material
    # Verifica se h informaes de textura e cria o n correspondente
    if "TEXTUREFILE" in properties:
        texture_file = properties["TEXTUREFILE"]
        texture_node = material.node_tree.nodes.new("ShaderNodeTexImage")
        texture_node.image = bpy.data.images.load(texture_file)
        texture_node.projection = 'BOX'
        mapping_node = material.node_tree.nodes.new("ShaderNodeMapping")
        mapping_node.vector_type = 'TEXTURE'
        mapping = "BOX"
        if "MAPPING" in properties:
            mapping = properties["MAPPING"]

        if "ESCALETEXTUREX" in properties:
            mapping_node.inputs[3].default_value[0] = float(properties["ESCALETEXTUREX"]) / (1 if mapping == "Planar" else 1000)
        if "ESCALETEXTUREY" in properties:  
            mapping_node.inputs[3].default_value[1] = float(properties["ESCALETEXTUREY"]) / (1 if mapping == "Planar" else 1000)
            mapping_node.inputs[3].default_value[2] = float(properties["ESCALETEXTUREY"]) / (1 if mapping == "Planar" else 1000)

        texture_coord_node = material.node_tree.nodes.new("ShaderNodeTexCoord")
        # Conectando Outros
        material.node_tree.links.new(texture_coord_node.outputs["Object"], mapping_node.inputs["Vector"])
        material.node_tree.links.new(mapping_node.outputs["Vector"], texture_node.inputs[0])
        # Conecta o n de textura ao n Principled BSDF
        material.node_tree.links.new(texture_node.outputs["Color"], principled_bsdf.inputs["Base Color"])
    
    # Verifica se a transparncia  maior que zero
    if 'TRANSPARENCY' in properties and float(properties['TRANSPARENCY']) > 0:
        material.use_screen_refraction = True
        material.refraction_depth = 0.003

# Funo para criar os materiais
def read_xml_file(filepath):
    bpy.ops.object.select_all(action='DESELECT')
    bpy.ops.object.select_all(action='SELECT')
    bpy.ops.object.editmode_toggle()
    bpy.ops.mesh.select_all(action='SELECT')
    bpy.ops.mesh.remove_doubles()
    bpy.ops.mesh.tris_convert_to_quads()
    bpy.ops.mesh.tris_convert_to_quads(shape_threshold=3.14159)
    bpy.ops.object.editmode_toggle()
    bpy.ops.object.select_all(action='DESELECT')

    tree = ET.parse(filepath)
    root = tree.getroot()
    
    # Criao dos materiais
    materials_list = root.find('MaterialsList')
    for material_element in materials_list.findall('Material'):
        material_name = material_element.get('NAME')
        material_id = material_element.get('ID')
        
        # Verifica se o material j existe
        material = bpy.data.materials.get(material_id)
        if not material:
            material = bpy.data.materials.new(name=material_id)
        
        # Define as propriedades do material
        properties = {}
        for prop_element in material_element:
            prop_name = prop_element.tag
            prop_value = prop_element.text
            properties[prop_name] = prop_value
            if prop_name == "COLORBASE":
                r = int(prop_element.get("R"))
                g = int(prop_element.get("G"))
                b = int(prop_element.get("B"))
                properties["COLORBASE"] = (r / 255, g / 255, b / 255, 1.0)
        
        apply_material_properties(material, properties)
    
    # Aplicao dos materiais aos objetos
    objects_list = root.find('ObjectsList')
    for object_element in objects_list.findall('Object'):
        object_name = object_element.get('NAME')
        object_type = object_element.get('TYPE')
        
        # Verifica se o objeto existe na cena
        obj = bpy.data.objects.get(object_name)
        if obj:
            materials = object_element.findall('Material')
            for material_element in materials:
                material_id = material_element.get('ID')
                material = bpy.data.materials.get(material_id)
                if material:
                    obj.data.materials.append(material)

# Funo de callback para o boto de abrir o arquivo XML
def open_file_callback(filepath):
    read_xml_file(filepath)

# Classe do painel de interface
class XMLImporterPanel(bpy.types.Panel):
    bl_idname = "OBJECT_PT_xml_importer"
    bl_label = "XML Importer"
    bl_space_type = "VIEW_3D"
    bl_region_type = "UI"
    bl_category = "XML Import"

    def draw(self, context):
        layout = self.layout

        row = layout.row()
        row.operator("wm.xml_file_selector", text="Open XML File")

# Classe do operador para selecionar o arquivo XML
class XMLFileSelectorOperator(bpy.types.Operator):
    bl_idname = "wm.xml_file_selector"
    bl_label = "Select XML File"
    bl_description = "Open an XML file with material information"
    filepath: bpy.props.StringProperty(subtype="FILE_PATH")
    # Definindo o filtro do arquivo
    filter_glob: bpy.props.StringProperty(default="*.xml", options={"HIDDEN"})
    def execute(self, context):
        open_file_callback(self.filepath)
        return {'FINISHED'}

    def invoke(self, context, event):
        context.window_manager.fileselect_add(self)
        return {'RUNNING_MODAL'}

# Registrar os tipos
classes = (
    XMLImporterPanel,
    XMLFileSelectorOperator
)

# Registrar as classes no Blender
def register():
    for cls in classes:
        bpy.utils.register_class(cls)

# Remover as classes do Blender
def unregister():
    for cls in classes:
        bpy.utils.unregister_class(cls)

# Executar o registro ao iniciar o script
if __name__ == "__main__":
    register()

#note, kill previous mpv before starting a new process.

import mysql.connector

class Database:
    def __init__(self, host, username, password, database):
        self.host = host
        self.username = username
        self.password = password
        self.database = database
        self.connection = None

    def connect(self):
        self.connection = mysql.connector.connect(
            host=self.host,
            user=self.username,
            password=self.password,
            database=self.database
        )

    def disconnect(self):
        if self.connection:
            self.connection.close()

    def execute_query(self, query, values=None):
        cursor = self.connection.cursor()
        if values:
            cursor.execute(query, values)
        else:
            cursor.execute(query)
        self.connection.commit()
        return cursor

class User:
    def __init__(self, id, name, email):
        self.id = id
        self.name = name
        self.email = email

class CRUDApp:
    def __init__(self, db_config):
        self.db_config = db_config
        self.db = None

    def initialize_db(self):
        self.db = Database(**self.db_config)
        self.db.connect()

    def close_db(self):
        self.db.disconnect()

    def create_user(self, name, email):
        query = "INSERT INTO users (name, email) VALUES (%s, %s)"
        values = (name, email)
        self.db.execute_query(query, values)

    def read_users(self):
        query = "SELECT id, name, email FROM users"
        result = self.db.execute_query(query)
        users = []
        for row in result:
            user = User(*row)
            users.append(user)
        return users

    def update_user(self, user_id, name, email):
        query = "UPDATE users SET name = %s, email = %s WHERE id = %s"
        values = (name, email, user_id)
        self.db.execute_query(query, values)

    def delete_user(self, user_id):
        query = "DELETE FROM users WHERE id = %s"
        values = (user_id,)
        self.db.execute_query(query, values)

# Start Here
if __name__ == "__main__":
    db_config = {
        "host": "localhost",
        "username": "your_username",
        "password": "your_password",
        "database": "your_database_name"
    }

    app = CRUDApp(db_config)
    app.initialize_db()

    # Create a user
    app.create_user("John Doe", "john.doe@example.com")

    # Read users
    users = app.read_users()
    for user in users:
        print(f"ID: {user.id}, Name: {user.name}, Email: {user.email}")

    # Update a user
    user_id_to_update = 1
    app.update_user(user_id_to_update, "Jane Smith", "jane.smith@example.com")

    # Delete a user
    user_id_to_delete = 2
    app.delete_user(user_id_to_delete)

    app.close_db()
